{"tid":338152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇鐘意畫畫既朋友仔？","createTime":"2017-07-28T02:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T05:01:45.000Z","uid":131630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22ca01e4d9d33eafb2122b95badbcc5d6d33c7c9","tid":338152,"uid":131630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"唔知你地有冇念過想將畫畫當成職業呢？<br />\n以我所知香港都多成功既插畫師<br />\n插畫師:謝曬皮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/102857_72075856abc2fc1124bb1a539b011e4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F102857_72075856abc2fc1124bb1a539b011e4d.jpg&h=e3ceac15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原網址: <a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2013/05/31/40060/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2013%2F05%2F31%2F40060%2F&d=bike7XMNu5WEBsN6JscLtjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=262851ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2013/05/31/40060/</a><br />\n但係我既畫風完全係另一回事<br />\n所以畫畫係香港係咪冇前境。。？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我目標係好似以下3位Artist <br />\n靠自己既畫就有收入 又做到自己鐘意做既野<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/103238_74faaea9369ea8dab5c672e2d4865bc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F103238_74faaea9369ea8dab5c672e2d4865bc1.jpg&h=5474301a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我既作品<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/103922_e4a0b813fd3aee3a7c9428fc66080559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F103922_e4a0b813fd3aee3a7c9428fc66080559.jpg&h=414a6077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/103935_24d52257e41f2f3fec8c882398c7c95f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F103935_24d52257e41f2f3fec8c882398c7c95f.jpg&h=9ad07c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想問聲有冇人知個3位Artist佢地收入既來源？<br />\n應唔應該追夢 好迷網呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家比啲意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4599dcff5ac239bed7fbd19246318d1d8ea83c13","tid":338152,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:49:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35b223824ffa90fce2c9ea45195362af1cdb949f","tid":338152,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"香港得圖文插畫先紅得起<br />\n真正有畫功既講出黎都冇人識"},{"pid":"9c8c1fab072dc63254aa937d5c17fb069feb8f73","tid":338152,"uid":78758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:51:18.000Z","msg":"Michael Chang<br />\nFCP"},{"pid":"9e69bf2ec809d86f18ec13aaab74a23330d30bda","tid":338152,"uid":78758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:58:03.000Z","msg":"開心share 慢慢睇<br />\n<br />\nsnnn / たえ<br />\n浪人 / Lownine <br />\nKekai kotaki<br />\nBen Lo<br />\nASK<br />\n村田蓮爾<br />\nRedjuice<br />\nMiv4t"},{"pid":"7e3f8f9ea797d61158475d778320f47d0122a3eb","tid":338152,"uid":131630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港得圖文插畫先紅得起<br />\n真正有畫功既講出黎都冇人識</blockquote><br />\n好Sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但都係事實"},{"pid":"789748b09b0f61a971730bf7dc35b4f96ceccad4","tid":338152,"uid":131630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開心share 慢慢睇<br />\n<br />\nsnnn / たえ<br />\n浪人 / Lownine <br />\nKekai kotaki<br />\nBen Lo<br />\nASK<br />\n村田蓮爾<br />\nRedjuice<br />\nMiv4t</blockquote><br />\n神作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6870902973bbb10f263ee8daa4584c56308ed234","tid":338152,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply